reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select 
rlt.RLTSHP_ID AS RELID, 
sub_acc.TAX_RPT_TIN_NO as SSN,
count(distinct sub_acc_svc.ACCT_SVC_TY_CD) as accountsCount

from PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc
join PROD.SUBACCT_SVC_12569 sub_acc_svc on sub_acc.ACCT_ID = sub_acc_svc.ACCT_ID
join PROD.RLTSHP_13120 as rlt on rlt.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID = acctgrp.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID
join PROD.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_DTL_13088 as acctgrp on acctgrp.ACCT_ID=sub_acc.ACCT_ID
where
rlt.RLTSHP_ID = rlt.RLTSHP_ID
and sub_acc.TAX_RPT_TIN_NO = sub_acc.TAX_RPT_TIN_NO
and sub_acc.BR_NO in (4369)
and sub_acc.ACCT_OWN_SUBTY_CD is not NULL
and sub_acc.ACCT_CLS_UT is NULL
and sub_acc_svc.ACCT_SVC_TY_CD in ('SE', 'AV', 'GD', 'GE', 'UM')
and sub_acc_svc.ISO_CTRY_CD='US'
group by rlt.RLTSHP_ID, sub_acc.TAX_RPT_TIN_NO
having count(distinct sub_acc_svc.ACCT_SVC_TY_CD)>1
